%define        gemname graphql

Name:          gem-graphql
Version:       1.13.12
Release:       alt1
Summary:       A plain-Ruby implementation of GraphQL
License:       MIT
Group:         Development/Ruby
Url:           https://graphql-ruby.org/
Vcs:           https://github.com/rmosolgo/graphql-ruby.git
